---
// Newsletter CTA, on the desk below the sheet (plan U3).
---

<div class="post-cta">
  <h3>Get more like this</h3>
  <p>Subscribe to the CC4.Marketing newsletter for updates, guides, and practical AI marketing tips.</p>
  <a href="https://cc4marketing.substack.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-btn">Subscribe on Substack</a>
</div>

<style>
  .post-cta {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 32px;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink-100);
    background: var(--tint-rust-1);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4em;
    color: var(--ink-100);
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--ink-70);
    max-width: 46ch;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    background: var(--rust);
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-mustard);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    transform: translate(-3px, -3px);
    box-shadow: 9px 9px 0 var(--mustard);
  }

  .cta-btn:focus-visible {
    outline: 3px solid var(--ink-100);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .cta-btn,
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transition: none;
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>
